    Our Mission

    Democratize the Special Education

    Watch Our TEDx Talk

    We believe that education is a basic human right and are determined to improve our work until proper special education is available and accessible to each and every household in need.

    Inclusive education means that all students attend and are welcomed by their neighbourhood schools in age-appropriate, regular classes and are supported to learn, contribute and participate in all aspects of the life of the school.

    2019 Inclusive Education Association
